{"tid":1003265,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"友愛穆斯林 方濟各將成訪阿拉伯半島首位教宗","createTime":"2019-01-31T13:40:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-31T14:53:26.000Z","uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f31fe4c7cc237506b25558d32883d8dffb4084ef","tid":1003265,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T13:40:39.000Z","msg":"（中央社梵蒂岡31日綜合外電報導）教宗方濟各（Francis）下月3日將成為首位訪問阿拉伯半島的教宗，在搭起與伊斯蘭社會的橋梁上再邁出重要一步，並證明了跨宗教對話是方濟各的基本原則。<br />\n<br />\n羅馬天主教會教宗長久以來與穆斯林世界關係錯綜複雜，但阿根廷籍的方濟各因友愛的言語和欲化解宗教分歧而受到關注。<br />\n<br />\n在羅馬教廷阿拉伯與伊斯蘭研究中心教授伊斯蘭和基督教關係的柯帝尼（Valentino Cottini）說：「教宗方濟各和前教宗本篤十六世（Benedict XVI）不同，他喜好和人接觸。」<br />\n<br />\n方濟各不斷呼籲要歡迎難民，當中許多人是穆斯林，這讓他在穆斯林社會獲得支持，他也曾讓3個穆斯林難民家庭搭上教宗專機，從希臘列士波斯島（Lesbos）到羅馬展開新生活。（譯者：蔡佳伶/核稿：劉淑琴）1080131<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/201901310241.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Faopl%2F201901310241.aspx&d=WPS43JJkpORccPZf4osG%2FcrrJHX4TENqAnNRziDaZDA%3D&h=e2bca2d1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/201901310241.aspx</a>"},{"pid":"0f59adbe6af4026ae69bb72e1a14d96ed0568674","tid":1003265,"uid":141151,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T14:44:52.000Z","msg":"基督教世界終極臥底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a60b52445fe54e61c0fc97a0561c2a38a603849","tid":1003265,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T14:50:46.000Z","msg":"分分鐘無命"},{"pid":"45f6331545830c0fb114a0da0ecbc25aaa2636de","tid":1003265,"uid":52215,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T14:53:26.000Z","msg":"一陣係阿拉伯俾人冧底<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}